<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- أَوْ عِنْدَ الْقَائِلِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">* وَكَذَا الْقَوْلُ فِي:</span> <span class="c1">"الأشْهَرِ"</span>، وَ<span class="c1">"الأظْهَرِ"</span>، وَ<span class="c1">"الأوْلَى"</span>، وَ<span class="c1">"الأقْيَسِ"</span>، وَنَحْوِ ذَلِكَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">* وَقَوْلُهُمْ:</span> <span class="c1">"وَقِيلَ <span class="c2">(١)</span> "</span>:<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">فَإِنَّهُ قَدْ يَكُونُ:</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- رِوَايَةً بِالإِيمَاءِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- أَوْ وَجْهًا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- أَوْ تَخْرِيجًا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- أَوِ احْتِمَالًا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>* ثُمَ <span class="c1">"الرِّوَايَةُ"</span>:<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">قَدْ تكُونُ:</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- نَصًّا.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- أَوْ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> إِيمَاءً.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- أَوْ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> تَخْرِيجًا مِنَ الأصْحَابِ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) في (ب): قيل.<br>(٢) من (أ) و (غ) و (ظ)، وفي (ب): و.<br>(٣) من (أ) و (ص) و (ظ) و (غ)، وفي (ب): و.</p> </div>